name: The Birdcage
directions: Two toilets, both gender neutral. The first (with a single stall and urinals) is just past the bar on the right. For the second (with two stalls) go past the first, down the steps, through the back room - it's at the far end.
comment:
The Birdcage is a bar, so you'd probably need to stop for a drink. However, it is open all day - so you could just have a tea/coffee.

Also, some evenings the back room is used for performances - so there is only the single stall and urinals.
